  "text": "For backbone resonance assignments, the 3D HNCA and NOE-SY-15 N-HSQC spectra were supplemented by [ 15 N, 1 H]-HSQC spectra of selectively isotope-labelled samples and samples with sitedirected mutations. The assignments of NS2Bc residues were supported by recording 2D BEST-TROSY-HNCO spectra [CITATION_1] .",
